summary:
PELANGI (short for Pelayanan Ngasem Terintegrasi) is here to make life in Ngasem easier and more connected. Launched in 2023, this app is all about streamlining access and offering smart solutions for the community.
&ldquo;PELANGI is crafted to improve the quality of life for Ngasem residents and boost the connection between the government and its people using the latest in digital tech.&rdquo;
Check Out PELANGI&rsquo;s Cool Features Feature Description Administrative Registration Easily register for essential documents like KTP, KK, and more right from the app.
